Subject: [PATCH 63/63] =?UTF-8?q?web-app:=20player=20controls=20in=20two?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20rows=20=E2=80=94=20waveform=20full-width,=20time=20+=20speed?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20below?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

The seek/waveform row no longer shares its line with the time display and
speed pill: right of the play button, the waveform takes the full width
and a meta row below carries elapsed/total (start) and the speed pill
(end) — the usual messenger layout. Applies to all three surfaces via the
shared CustomAudioControls (bubbles, mini-player, recorder preview);
markup-only regroup, all behavior (seek input, drag guard, aria) is
untouched.
---
 .../src/components/AudioPlayer/index.tsx      | 114 ++++++++++--------
 .../components/AudioPlayer/styles.module.scss |  13 ++
 2 files changed, 74 insertions(+), 53 deletions(-)

diff --git a/packages/frontend/src/components/AudioPlayer/index.tsx b/packages/frontend/src/components/AudioPlayer/index.tsx
index f900ef187..23113a1fc 100644
--- a/packages/frontend/src/components/AudioPlayer/index.tsx
